thread.title: Tracey Bainbrigge

author: Tracey Bainbrigge
title: Tracey Bainbrigge
text: My husband and I were lucky to have Janet Rayner as our Account Manager. Janet is truly a professional as she handled all of our dealings with the utmost of care. We had dealings both in Australia and the UK and Janet always made herself available and had solutions for any concerns we had. I would highly recommend Janet, along with TORfx to look after any currency dealings.
